; Regression test for issue #2395
; --ignore-diacritics flag should allow ASCII search terms to match
; accented/diacritic characters in payee names, account names, etc.

2024-01-01 Boulangerie spécialité
    Expenses:Café    10 EUR
    Assets:Checking

2024-01-15 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    20 EUR
    Assets:Checking

2024-02-01 Résumé Services
    Expenses:Office    50 EUR
    Assets:Checking

; Test 1: Payee search with @, ASCII pattern matching accented payee
test reg --ignore-diacritics @specialite --columns=80 -> 0
24-Jan-01 Boulangerie spécial.. Expenses:Café                10 EUR       10 EUR
                                Assets:Checking             -10 EUR            0
end test

; Test 2: Account search, ASCII pattern matching accented account
test reg --ignore-diacritics Cafe --columns=80 -> 0
24-Jan-01 Boulangerie spécial.. Expenses:Café                10 EUR       10 EUR
end test

; Test 3: Payee search with accented pattern matching accented payee
test reg --ignore-diacritics @Resume --columns=80 -> 0
24-Feb-01 Résumé Services       Expenses:Office              50 EUR       50 EUR
                                Assets:Checking             -50 EUR            0
end test

; Test 4: Without --ignore-diacritics, ASCII should NOT match accented
test reg @specialite --columns=80 -> 0
end test
